topic.title: Multi-lane Interface Skew

body.p: The tables below provide the maximum transmit skew and minimum receive skew tolerance between any two SERDES lanes on each high speed SERDES Bank. If an interface spans SERDES banks then additional skew will be introduced. Skew variations are also shown, when applicable.
